Summary: While photographing object wasn't there, appeared after download.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking photos in Cape Porpoise, Maine. The object wasn't visible when I shot the photo but appeared after it was downloaded. What's interesting is I took this photo and then turned slightly to the right and shot another photo (which I've attached) and it wasn't there. I don't remember when it was, maybe September or October of 2000.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Kennebunkport
This sighting has never been favorited.
